name: Dorris and Giordano
overview:
Dorris and Giordano is a law firm that specializes in the areas of Corporate & Transactional, Litigation and Estates & Family Law providing expertise in Arizona and the Southwest region.

Our lawyers have extensive years of experience handling lawsuits and cases representing an individual or group, whether public or private companies in numerous sectors. With the wide range of practice areas, our attorneys can apply an effective approach in handling a case for our clients.
